 3a+b=0,\ a+6b=1. 
 a=-\frac{1}{17},\ b=\frac{3}{17}. 
 (1+3\sqrt{2})x=1-5\sqrt{2} \iff x=(1+3\sqrt{2})^{-1}(1-5\sqrt{2}), 
 x=\frac{1}{17}(-1+3\sqrt{2})(1-5\sqrt{2})=-\frac{31}{17}+\frac{8}{17}\sqrt{2}. 
